# ==============================================
# Hotspot Helsinki - Environment Variables
# ==============================================

# ----------------------------------------------
# Google Places API
# ----------------------------------------------
# Get your API key from: https://console.cloud.google.com/
# Enable: Places API, Maps JavaScript API
VITE_GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=your_google_places_api_key_here
GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=your_google_places_api_key_here

# Note: Use the same key for both VITE_ (client) and server-side
# VITE_ prefix exposes to client, server-side key stays protected
# ----------------------------------------------
# Vercel KV (Optional - for caching)
# ----------------------------------------------
# These are automatically provided by Vercel when you add KV storage
# Leave empty for local development - app will work without caching
KV_REST_API_URL=
KV_REST_API_TOKEN=
KV_REST_API_READ_ONLY_TOKEN=

# ==============================================
# Data Sources
# ==============================================
# Free public APIs (no keys required):
#   - LinkedEvents API (City of Helsinki)
#   - MyHelsinki Open API
#
# With Google Places API key:
#   - Venue details (opening hours, ratings, photos)
#   - Enhanced location information
#   - Nearby places finder
# ==============================================

